00123     virtual SUMOReal getEffort(const E* const e, SUMOReal t) const {
00124         SUMOReal value;
00125         if (MSNet::getInstance()->getWeightsStorage().retrieveExistingEffort(e, 0, t, value)) {
00126             return value;
00127         }
00128         const MSLane* const l = e->getLanes()[0];
00129         return l->getLength() / l->getMaxSpeed();

00135     virtual void compute(const E* from, const E* to, const MSVehicle* const vehicle,
00136                          SUMOTime msTime, std::vector<const E*> &into) {
00137         UNUSED_PARAMETER(vehicle);
00138         const SUMOReal time = STEPS2TIME(msTime);
00139         // get structures to reuse
00140         std::vector<bool> *visited = myReusableEdgeLists.getFreeInstance();
00141         if (visited == 0) {
00142             visited = new std::vector<bool>(myNoE, false);
00143         } else {
00144             for (size_t i = 0; i < myNoE; i++) {
00145                 (*visited)[i] = false; // too slow? !!!
00146             }
00147         }
00148         EdgeInfoCont* storage = myReusableEdgeInfoLists.getFreeInstance();
00149         if (storage == 0) {
00150             storage = new EdgeInfoCont(myNoE);
00151         }
00152         storage->reset();
00153 
00154         // check the nodes
00155         if (from == 0 || to == 0) {
00156             throw std::exception();
00157         }
00158 
00159         // begin computation
00160         std::priority_queue < EdgeInfo*,
00161             std::vector<EdgeInfo*>,
00162             EdgeInfoByEffortComperator > frontierList;
00163         // add begin node
00164         const E* actualKnot = from;
00165         if (from != 0) {
00166             EdgeInfo* ei = storage->add(actualKnot, 0, 0);
00167             frontierList.push(ei);
00168         }
00169         bool isFirstIteration = true;
00170 
00171         // loop
00172         while (!frontierList.empty()) {
00173             // use the node with the minimal length
00174             EdgeInfo* minimumKnot = frontierList.top();
00175             const E* minEdge = minimumKnot->edge;
00176             frontierList.pop();
00177             // check whether the destination node was already reached
00178             if ((minEdge == to) && (!isFirstIteration)) {
00179                 buildPathFrom(minimumKnot, into);
00180                 clearTemporaryStorages(visited, storage);
00181                 return;
00182             }
00183             (*visited)[minEdge->getNumericalID()] = true;
00184             const SUMOReal effort = (SUMOReal)(minimumKnot->effort + getEffort(minEdge, time + minimumKnot->effort));
00185             // check all ways from the node with the minimal length
00186             unsigned int i = 0;
00187             const unsigned int length_size = minEdge->getNoFollowing();
00188             for (i = 0; i < length_size; i++) {
00189                 const E* help = minEdge->getFollower(i);
00190 
00191                 if ((!(*visited)[help->getNumericalID()] && effort < storage->getEffort(help))
00192                         || (help == to)) {
00193 //                    if (help!=from) {
00194                     frontierList.push(storage->add(help, effort, minimumKnot));
00195 //                    }
00196                 }
00197             }
00198 
00199             isFirstIteration = false;
00200         }
00201         clearTemporaryStorages(visited, storage);
00202     }

00205     SUMOReal recomputeCosts(const std::vector<const E*> &edges, const MSVehicle* const v, SUMOTime msTime) const {
00206         UNUSED_PARAMETER(v);
00207         const SUMOReal time = STEPS2TIME(msTime);
00208         SUMOReal costs = 0;
00209         for (typename std::vector<const E*>::const_iterator i = edges.begin(); i != edges.end(); i++) {
00210             costs += getEffort(*i, time + costs);
00211         }
00212         return costs;
00213     }

00217     void buildPathFrom(EdgeInfo* rbegin, std::vector<const E*> &edges) {
00218         std::deque<const E*> tmp;
00219         EdgeInfo* last = rbegin;
00220         while (rbegin != 0) {
00221             tmp.push_front((E*) rbegin->edge);  // !!!
00222             rbegin = rbegin->prev;
00223             if (rbegin == last) {
00224                 tmp.push_front((E*) rbegin->edge);
00225                 break;
00226             }
00227         }
00228         std::copy(tmp.begin(), tmp.end(), std::back_inserter(edges));
00229     }
